language Essence 1.3

given numItems : int(1..)
given itemSize : matrix indexed by [int(1..numItems)] of int(1..)
given binCap : int(1..)

letting maxBins be numItems

find packing : partition from int(1..numItems)

minimising |parts(packing)|

such that
    forAll bin in parts(packing) .
        (sum item in bin . itemSize[item]) <= binCap
